#Bachelor Basha vara calculator🏠

A simple Python script to calculate the per-person monthly cost in a shared bachelor house or mess.

---

## 📌 Features

- Takes inputs for:
  - House rent
  - Monthly food cost
  - Electricity bill
  - WiFi bill
  - House help (Bua) cost
  - Garbage cleaning cost
  - Gas bill
  - Total number of people

- Calculates total monthly expense
- Splits the total cost equally for each person

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1️⃣ Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/sharatpsd/Bachelor Basha vara calculator.git
